arStrings.szText: Your {c_important}Minions{/c} deal {c_random}[Affix_Value_2|%x|]{/c} increased damage, but each one drains {c_number}[Affix_Value_1]{/c} Essence from you per second. If you have no active {c_important}Minions{/c}, the damage increase applies to you instead, and you lose {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} Essence per second.
